{"tid":1650722,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"李家超：警方公眾地方核實市民身份要求除口罩屬常理","createTime":"2019-10-13T06:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T08:59:44.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5668b5068c9c62ff5a248d6a75452415b0220db9","tid":1650722,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:03:26.000Z","msg":"保安局局長李家超表示，在考慮推行《禁蒙面法》時，已經預計到部分市民會反對。他出席一個電視節目時說，在《禁蒙面法》實施下，警員在公眾地方核實市民身份時，對方要移除口罩或蒙面物品是「常理」。<br />\n<br />\n被問到有警員在施放催淚彈後，即時要求在場記者除下面罩核實身份是否不恰當，李家超回應指，實際情況各有不同，希望雙方互相尊重、體諒。<br />\n<br />\n對於警隊是否成為整個事件的磨心，李家超說，香港的問題不是靠警隊執法能解決，但警隊必須制止暴力，認為政治問題要靠整個社會一同解決，而政府是責無旁貸。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%A0%B8%E5%AF%A6%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%99%A4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%B1%AC%E5%B8%B8%E7%90%86-050420615.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2585%25AC%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2596%25B9%25E6%25A0%25B8%25E5%25AF%25A6%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B0%2591%25E8%25BA%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BD%25E8%25A6%2581%25E6%25B1%2582%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%25BD%25A9%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%25B8%25B8%25E7%2590%2586-050420615.html&d=BELmNDq%2B1pqro4agOzjMGajD3B6m7wr0JF9t5bmmazk%3D&h=f1d94682\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85-%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%B9%E5%85%AC%E7%9C%BE%E5%9C%B0%E6%96%B9%E6%A0%B8%E5%AF%A6%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E8%BA%AB%E4%BB%BD%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%99%A4%E5%8F%A3%E7%BD%A9%E5%B1%AC%E5%B8%B8%E7%90%86-050420615.html</a>"},{"pid":"9bcf7980154435144b972658cc2c37b5999da167","tid":1650722,"uid":322141,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T06:04:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fa90a9c6a13094af6bdd250539054ffd06840631","tid":1650722,"uid":49336,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"repl